{"tid":1609870,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"教你點樣同中共長期抗衡","createTime":"2019-10-01T15:42:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T03:24:47.000Z","uid":132544,"like":9,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0a9103b82e577f9f75378bdbabc91b76a24a077b","tid":1609870,"uid":132544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:42:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">就係扑多啲野</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好用套！</span><br />\n<br />\n香港雖然唔係個生存嘅好地方<br />\n<br />\n但係要令香港仲有香港人<br />\n<br />\n就一定唔好怕辛苦<br />\n<br />\n生多幾個<br />\n<br />\n將香港人嘅良好基因遺傳落去<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港一定要有香港人！</span>"},{"pid":"5e81a954fab758ee72f603465a794f9d19fa8662","tid":1609870,"uid":132544,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:44:19.000Z","msg":"唔好覺得好似害咗下一代咁<br />\n<br />\n你唔撚生仔害咗成個香港添呀"},{"pid":"757074a464d9ed7d8b5c63de512fb671671a0e53","tid":1609870,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:44:20.000Z","msg":"經過今日 殺警都唔係問題 ！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1609207\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1609207</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7fe2438122b2b5fc6157ffab7f84bda234986394","tid":1609870,"uid":213647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:44:31.000Z","msg":"要求馬上籌組臨時政府<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1609431\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1609431</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n香港人，諗下點樣贏"},{"pid":"73d772349977c5e82dbe28685c5867d115caffbd","tid":1609870,"uid":132544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:44:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8858a97024cb5296f76a07bea9da67b0c11f42f7","tid":1609870,"uid":132544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:46:54.000Z","msg":"如果香港無咗香港人<br />\n<br />\n咁香港仲係咪香港<br />\n<br />\n如果香港嘅香港人比其他民族少<br />\n<br />\n香港仲係咪香港？"},{"pid":"4690b8a4083a4f23a905eb6a33670212ff2e7d9a","tid":1609870,"uid":132544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:48:43.000Z","msg":"要香港中嘅香港人多過大陸人<br />\n<br />\n首先，唔好死<br />\n<br />\n第二，唔好比啲大陸人配種，最好閹撚晒佢地<br />\n<br />\n第三，生多啲香港人"},{"pid":"66ca59d6f3a32533fbad8136673bf03b15f107db","tid":1609870,"uid":132544,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:50:37.000Z","msg":"香港人係一個民族<br />\n<br />\n我地係命運嘅共同體<br />\n<br />\n請大家唔好令自己滅族"},{"pid":"6d8eda40e9e325f2c2de040a1ececa231ff655ab","tid":1609870,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:20:17.000Z","msg":"我都想呀"},{"pid":"2a56ace666e9094a27554743dc14ab4d797b797c","tid":1609870,"uid":44856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:38:42.000Z","msg":"毒撚冇女<br />\n完<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e37d4b3267a51d75d9c712a4fff7a06e8da8524","tid":1609870,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:05:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去兩個月，大家既生活都過得好壓抑。有人係依兩個月之間同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不要質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FE2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVpMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=e0ac50f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5d6979cc07ade6863f3246c01c90a5cd2af4b98","tid":1609870,"uid":147242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:16:10.000Z","msg":"ok<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ead4ce974a9bcc1cde6225ff70c5c2cba24e53e3","tid":1609870,"uid":158372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:50:10.000Z","msg":"生完唔撚使養咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c2e7ea35e5755c3f41db5763d43d495a9766e76","tid":1609870,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:21:52.000Z","msg":"之前仲話無希望唔生仔 依家就話無希望生多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c49b91d22055a9a12cd1842a21efc3b93615d0b1","tid":1609870,"uid":319806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:24:47.000Z","msg":"大家行行企企吃花生 民主自然會嚟 強國會給我們民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}